bilingual.target: 请在周五前确认你是否出席。

bilingual.source: What percent was the attendance at the meeting?
bilingual.target: 这次会议的出席率是百分之几？

bilingual.source: The concert had a record attendance this year.
bilingual.target: 今年音乐会的出席人数创下了记录。

bilingual.source: Attendance at the meeting was compulsorily enforced.
bilingual.target: 会议的出席率是强制地执行的。

bilingual.source: The attendance at the meeting was higher than expected.
bilingual.target: 会议的出席人数比预期的要多。

bilingual.source: The teacher took attendance at the beginning of the class.
bilingual.target: 老师在课堂开始时点了出席。

bilingual.source: The falloff in attendance at the event was disappointing.
bilingual.target: 活动出席人数的减少令人失望。

bilingual.source: High attendance is crucial for the success of the event.
bilingual.target: 高出席率对活动的成功至关重要。

bilingual.source: Please confirm your attendance by replying to this email.
bilingual.target: 请通过回复此邮件确认您的出席。

yingyinNormal.en: Is it time? It is. Father, but I did not advise your attendance.
yingyinNormal.zh: 到时候了吗？是的。父皇，但是我不建议您出席。

yingyinNormal.en: Every time we've unveiled a new asset, attendance has spiked.
yingyinNormal.zh: 每次我们推出一个新的资产的时候，入场率都会飙升。

yingyinNormal.en: I don't object to the concept of a deity, but I'm baffled by the notion of one that takes attendance.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我并不反对神的概念，但实在不理解上教堂还得点名。

由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2015-2022年全国卷高考试卷，包括阅读、完形、单选、填空、听力、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。
